rial; font-size:12pt"> operational procedures, such as the Guidance Note for Environmental and Social Impact Assessment and Performance Standards </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 9.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">We are </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">developing a disability assessment toolkit for our staff to use within the operations.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="6" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 33.01pt; padding-left:2.99pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Partnership and Consultation</span></li></ol><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Our work greatly benefits from our formal and informal partnerships, with development institutions and donor countries</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">We participate at international fora, such as the UN High Level Meeting on Disability and Development and the Conf</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">e</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">rence of State Parties</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> for the UN Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilit</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">i</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">es</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family